{"tid":372730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[以德報怨]Uber澳門重開 推三天義載","createTime":"2017-08-24T13:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T02:42:28.000Z","uid":51271,"like":106,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f01084124991f3639becff7260f4e4be75de6918","tid":372730,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:50:28.000Z","msg":"呢招高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1503582031721&amp;issue=20170824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1503582031721%26issue%3D20170824&d=qm%2FKAUzScOk9DORplP4uFNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8dff105f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1503582031721&amp;issue=20170824</a><br />\n<br />\n颱風「天鴿」昨日橫掃澳門，原本已撤出澳門的Uber表示，澳門經歷嚴重風災，部份交通工具受破壞，故決定今天晚上9時重開Uber App，在未來的三天，舉行義載，方便民眾出行。<br />\n<br />\nUber 發言人表示，由於這次是義務提供服務，並不會收取酬，但提醒市民留給有急需的市民預約叫車。集團澳門總經理盧綺雯表示，颱風天鴿肆虐澳門，希望在艱難時間，為澳門出一分力，並感激司機夥伴的支持，在短時間內響應義載。"},{"pid":"6db0290a1a4200a5b22ca0f871e1c1b216ed42a9","tid":372730,"uid":30873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:51:37.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c50cd8355875deac531b080bcf72bb2b963138","tid":372730,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff569d4aeeb23f854ebcfd1960f7e437c641b0d6","tid":372730,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f220645a0bcefa5a4bff5e3e20159af6262f114","tid":372730,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{